The Pasta is made with premium durum wheat semolina. It is then prepared in the true artisan methods of a long time ago, extruded in bronze and exceptional flavor and texture. The pasta sauces are classic of any Mediterranean sicilian diet as they unify taste and nutritional content in order to offer a balanced healthy meal.
Campo D'Oro high-end selection of egg pastas and tomato sauce are imported from Sicily- Italy, where each exquisitely completed nest of pasta or jar of tomatoes sauces are created by skilled local Italian artisans and lovingly wrapped. This package, which expertly resembles the Italian flag, combines common pasta ingredients with delicious sauces for a complete meal.
Ideal for Corporative Gourmet Basket, for any Holidays (Thanksgiving, Christmas Gifts, Valentines, Mothers and Father‚Äôs Day). Also great for your favorite home chef's birthday.
Product of Italy, 100% Natural, Non-GMO, no additives, no preservatives.
CAMPO D'ORO: with more than 32 years has been producing a wide range of food specialties that reflect the Sicilian Culinary tradition. All raw material are processed by artisan methods.
